# Church Multi-Tenant Reporting System
## Solution Architecture Document

---

# 1. Project Overview

## Project Name
Church Multi-Tenant Reporting & Finance Management System

## Objective
To build a scalable web-based multi-tenant platform that allows different church installations (branches) to manage:

- Monthly attendance reports
- Financial records
- Dynamic weekly reporting
- Special event tracking
- Dashboard summaries
- PDF/Print-ready reports

Each branch operates independently using its own account while the Super Admin oversees all branches from a centralized dashboard.

---

# 2. Core Features

## 2.1 Multi-Tenant Branch Management

### Features
- Branch registration/login
- Role-based access control
- Data isolation per branch
- Super admin management panel

### Roles

| Role | Permissions |
|------|-------------|
| Super Admin | Access all branches |
| Branch Admin | Access only own branch |
| Accountant | Finance-only access |
| Secretary | Attendance/report access |

