# 3.1 Dynamic Calendar Module

## Objective
Automatically generate reporting weeks based on the selected month and year.

## Features
- Select month/year
- Auto-detect:
  - 4-week month
  - 5-week month
- Dynamic reporting tables

## Example

### February
- Week 1
- Week 2
- Week 3
- Week 4

### March
- Week 1
- Week 2
- Week 3
- Week 4
- Week 5

